:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4484:"<p>We have a fresh new lineup of <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule">free WordPress webinars</a> each Tuesday from <a href="http://webdesign.com">WebDesign.com</a>. With new topics each week, these sessions will walk through using iThemes Builder, Exchange, BackupBuddy and our upcoming WordPress Security Plugin.</p>\n<h2>Tuesday &#8211; Feb 18th, 2014</h2>\n<p><strong>iThemes Weekly Show</strong><br />\n11am CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-weekly-show-3" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Builder101: The Benefits of Using Style Manager</strong><br />\n1pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-builder-101-3" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>ExchangeTalk: Customer Management and Returns</strong><br />\n3pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-exchange-explained-3" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Discover Security: Using Two Backup Locations for Your BackupBuddy Files</strong><br />\n5pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-discover-security-3" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Tuesday &#8211; Feb 25th, 2014</h2>\n<p><strong>iThemes Weekly Show</strong><br />\n11am CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-weekly-show-4" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Builder101: Applying CSS to a Single Widget Area on a Multi-Widget Module</strong><br />\n1pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-builder-101-4" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>ExchangeTalk: Invoicing Your Clients</strong><br />\n3pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-exchange-explained-4" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Discover Security: How to Audit the Security of a Site</strong><br />\n5pm CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-discover-security-4" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Tuesday &#8211; March 4th, 2014</h2>\n<p><strong>iThemes Weekly Show</strong><br />\n11am CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-weekly-show-3-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Builder101: Building Your Site with Builder Views</strong><br />\n1pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-builder-101-3-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>ExchangeTalk: Updating Downloadable Product (Versioning)</strong><br />\n3pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-exchange-explained-3-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Discover Security: Top 5 Ways to Lock Down Your Site</strong><br />\n5pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-discover-security-3-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Tuesday &#8211; March 11th, 2014</h2>\n<p><strong>iThemes Weekly Show</strong><br />\n11am CST &#8211; <a style="font-size: medium; font-style: normal;" href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-weekly-show-4-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Builder101: Top 5 Ways to Maximize the HTML Module</strong><br />\n1pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-builder-101-4-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>ExchangeTalk: How to Use Free Products to Create Paying Customers</strong><br />\n3pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-exchange-explained-4-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<p><strong>Discover Security: How to Move a Site Between a Live Server and a Localhost</strong><br />\n5pm CST &#8211; <a href="http://webdesign.com/schedule/ithemes-tuesday-discover-security-4-2" target="_blank">REGISTER</a></p>\n<div class="content-callout">So register to attend one of these webinars — we’ll see you Tuesday!</div>\n<p>The post <a href="http://ithemes.com/2014/02/17/fresh-new-ithemes-tuesday-webinar-schedule/">A Fresh New iThemes Tuesday Webinar Schedule</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ithemes.com">iThemes</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:78:"http://ithemes.com/2014/02/17/fresh-new-ithemes-tuesday-webinar-schedule/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"iThemes Tuesday Webinar Replays: Exchange, Builder &amp; Security";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://ithemes.com/2014/02/12/ithemes-tuesday-webinar-replays-exchange-builder-security/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:97:"http://ithemes.com/2014/02/12/ithemes-tuesday-webinar-replays-exchange-builder-security/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base