";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Kristen Wright";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6497:"<p style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center;"><a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/bryant/"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21494" alt="bryant" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bryant.png" width="600" height="387" /></a></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px;">Introducing <a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/bryant/">Bryant</a>, a new iThemes Builder theme. In addition to features like the Builder Layout Editor and mobile-responsive design, Bryant features styles for post formats and Exchange, plus alternate module style options to mix up your page layouts.</p>\n<p><a class="btn green" href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/">Visit the Bryant Demo</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Theme Features Overview</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Exchange Styles for Store, Individual Products, Account &amp; Cart</li>\n<li>Responsive Mobile Menu</li>\n<li>Post Formats: Status, Quote, Image &amp; Standard</li>\n<li>Alternate Module Styles: Footer (Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Default), Widget Bar (Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Default), Navigation (Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Default) and Image (Full Window, No Spacing, Default)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Exchange Styles</h2>\n<p>Bryant includes theme-matching styles for Exchange, our <a href="http://ithemes.com/exchange">free ecommerce plugin</a>, so you can get started setting up your online shop.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21495" alt="Screen Shot 2014-01-30 at 10.02.16 AM" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Screen-Shot-2014-01-30-at-10.02.16-AM.png" width="1360" height="965" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 50px;">Responsive Mobile Navigation Menu</h2>\n<p>Bryant include a built-in responsive mobile menu for each navigation module style, so mobile visitors can easily navigate your site. To use this feature, add a navigation module to your page layout from the <a href="http://ithemes.com/codex/page/Creating_a_Builder_Layout">Builder Layout Editor</a>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21496" alt="navigation-module" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/navigation-module.png" width="671" height="477" /></p>\n<p>The mobile menu automatically appears when your site is accessed by devices with screen sizes that are less than 500px wide.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21511" alt="bryant-mobile" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/bryant-mobile.png" width="372" height="638" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 60px;">Post Format Support</h2>\n<p>Bryant takes advantage of Image, Quote, Status and Standard post formats by adding unique styling for each. When adding a post, just select the type of post format you&#8217;d like to apply to the post before publishing.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-20744" style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px;" alt="post-format" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/post-format.png" width="1060" height="634" /></p>\n<p><strong>Image</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21498" alt="image-post" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/image-post.png" width="937" height="464" /></p>\n<p><strong>Quote</strong></p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21500" alt="quote copy" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/quote-copy.png" width="859" height="430" /></p>\n<p><strong>Status</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21499" alt="status" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/status.png" width="704" height="355" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 60px;">Alternate Module Styles</h2>\n<p>Bryant includes <a href="http://ithemes.com/codex/page/Builder_Modules:_Alternate_Module_Styles">alternate module styles</a> to change up your page layouts, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Widget Bar</strong> &#8211; Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Transparent Background</li>\n<li><strong>Image</strong> &#8211; Full Window, No Spacing, Default</li>\n<li><strong>Footer</strong> &#8211; Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Default</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation</strong> &#8211; Dark Blue &#8211; Full Width, Default (both mobile-responsive)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To use these alternate module styles, select your preferred style from Style drop-down in the <strong>Modify Module Settings</strong> box when editing or creating a layout.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-20749" style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px;" alt="image-module" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/image-module.png" width="610" height="450" /></p>\n<h2>Layout Ideas</h2>\n<p>Check out the Bryant Demo Site for a few example page layout ideas, including <a href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/email-subscription/">Email Subscription</a>, <a href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/hero-banner/">Hero Banner</a> and <a href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/landing-page/">Landing Page</a>.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-21507" alt="hero-banner" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/hero-banner-1024x865.png" width="1024" height="865" /></p>\n<p>Check out <a href="http://ithemes.com/2013/12/04/new-builder-layouts-and-views-examples-and-ideas-for-your-builder-site/">this post </a>for more information on how to download and import these sample layouts into your Builder site.</p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Purchase &amp; Download Info</h2>\n<p>Bryant is available for purchase as part of the <a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/builder-theme/#theme-pricing">Builder Developer Pack</a>, <a href="http://ithemes.com/all-access-pass/">All Access Theme Pass</a> and <a href="http://ithemes.com/toolkit/">WordPress Web Designer&#8217;s Toolkit</a>. Bryant is also available as a <a href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/">stand-alone Builder theme</a>.</p>\n<div class="content-callout green">All current Builder Developer Pack, All Access Theme Pass and Toolkit members will find Bryant available now for immediate download from the <a href="http://ithemes.com/member/">iThemes Member Panel</a>.</div>\n<p><a class="btn green" href="http://demos.ithemes.com/bryant/">Get Bryant now</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://ithemes.com/2014/01/30/new-builder-theme-bryant/">A New Builder Theme: Bryant</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ithemes.com">iThemes</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://ithemes.com/2014/01/30/new-builder-theme-bryant/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"Sneak Peek: Sync + BackupBuddy Integration is Coming";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:87:"http://ithemes.com/2014/01/24/sneak-peek-sync-backupbuddy-integration-coming-next-week/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:96:"http://ithemes.com/2014/01/24/sneak-peek-sync-backupbuddy-integration-coming-next-week/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 24 Jan 2014 18:20:33 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"BackupBuddy";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"Sync";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27:"http://ithemes.com/?p=21400";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:606:"<p>We&#8217;ve been hard at work on an amazing new iThemes Sync dashboard update that features BackupBuddy and BackupBuddy Stash integration that&#8217;s slated for release soon. Oh, and as a bonus — the new Sync dashboard will also allow you to remotely activate and deactivate plugins on your Synced sites. It&#8217;s also fully mobile-responsive to make it [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href="http://ithemes.com/2014/01/24/sneak-peek-sync-backupbuddy-integration-coming-next-week/">Sneak Peek: Sync + BackupBuddy Integration is Coming</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ithemes.com">iThemes</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Kristen Wright";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5843:"<p>We&#8217;ve been hard at work on an amazing new <a href="http://ithemes.com/sync">iThemes Sync</a> dashboard update that features <a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/backupbuddy/">BackupBuddy</a> and <a href="http://ithemes.com/backupbuddy-stash/">BackupBuddy Stash</a> integration that&#8217;s slated for release soon.</p>\n<p>Oh, and as a bonus — the new Sync dashboard will also allow you to remotely activate and deactivate plugins on your Synced sites. It&#8217;s also fully mobile-responsive to make it easy to manage your WP sites on the go.</p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Sync + BackupBuddy &amp; BackupBuddy Stash Integration Features</h2>\n<p>With the new Sync Dashboard, not only will you be able to easily manage theme and plugin updates for your WordPress sites, you&#8217;ll also be able to manage BackupBuddy tasks, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make BackupBuddy backups of any Synced site using backup profiles</li>\n<li>Download your latest backup zip files</li>\n<li>View your active backup schedules, active profiles and destinations</li>\n<li>Manage/view BackupBuddy Stash storage for each Synced site</li>\n<li>View, download and delete Stash backups</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">New Sync Dashboard Home</h2>\n<p>Check out the new Sync Dashboard home. From here, you&#8217;ll be able to<strong> see each of your Synced site domains</strong>, plus <strong>quick links for Sync action options</strong> like logging into the site directly, refreshing the site, updating all available updates, hiding Sync and unsyncing the site.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21405" alt="new-stash-dashboard" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/new-stash-dashboard-1024x727.png" width="1024" height="727" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Individual Site View</h2>\n<p>The <strong>View Details</strong> link from the dashboard takes you to the individual site view. This view includes <strong>new Sync module sections</strong> to manage plugins, manage themes, Show/hide Sync and for BackupBuddy.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21401" alt="new-sync-backups" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/new-sync-backups.png" width="1212" height="894" /></p>\n<p>The BackupBuddy module includes the <strong>number of site edits since your last backup</strong>, plus a link to <strong>download your latest backup file</strong>. From here, you can even <strong>manually run a backup</strong>.</p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">More BackupBuddy Actions</h2>\n<p>To see even more BackupBuddy actions from the Sync dashboard, click the BackupBuddy tab at the top of the individual site page. From this screen, you can run a backup, but also <strong>view your current active backup profiles, destinations and your backups sent to Stash</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21402" alt="backupBuddy-sync" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/backupBuddy-sync.png" width="1225" height="974" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">New Sync Stash Dashboard</h2>\n<p>From the navigation on the left you can click <strong>My Stash</strong> to view your new Stash dashboard. From here, you can get a <strong>visual of your current BackupBuddy Stash storage usage</strong>, <strong>download each backup file that&#8217;s been sent to your BackupBuddy Stash account</strong> from your Synced sites, and <strong>delete these backup files</strong> from your Sync account.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class=" wp-image-21404 aligncenter" alt="new-stash-sync" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/new-stash-sync-1024x724.png" width="1024" height="724" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Bonus: Activate and Deactivate Plugins Remotely</h2>\n<p>In addition to BackupBuddy integration, the new Sync dashboard includes the ability to<strong> remotely activate and deactivate plugins and themes from the Sync Dashboard</strong>.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-21403" alt="activate-deactive-plugins-sync" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/activate-deactive-plugins-sync-1024x489.png" width="1024" height="489" /></p>\n<p>Visit any theme or plugin module from a Synced domain and select the plugin or theme you&#8217;d like to activate or deactivate.</p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Fully Mobile Responsive, Y&#8217;all</h2>\n<p>Last, but not least —<strong> the new Sync dashboard is completely mobile responsive.</strong> So if you need to run an update, make a backup or deactivate a plugin on the go, just log in to the Sync dashboard and perform any of these tasks quickly and easily.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-21423" alt="sync-mobile" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sync-mobile3.png" width="372" height="638" /></p>\n<h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Stay Tuned for the New Sync Dashboard Release Next Week</h2>\n<p>We&#8217;ll keep you posted about the new Sync dashboard release <a href="http://ithemes.com/subscribe/">via email</a>, <a href="http://twitter.com/ithemes">Twitter</a> and here on the blog. We&#8217;re really excited for you to take it for a spin— and that Sync will make managing all your WordPress sites so, so easy.</p>\n<p>And don&#8217;t forget to <a href="http://ithemes.com/member/panel/sync.php">go set up your Sync sites</a> — 10 sites are free for all current iThemes customers.</p>\n<p><a class="btn green" href="http://ithemes.com/member/panel/sync.php">Login to the Sync Dashboard</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://ithemes.com/2014/01/24/sneak-peek-sync-backupbuddy-integration-coming-next-week/">Sneak Peek: Sync + BackupBuddy Integration is Coming</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ithemes.com">iThemes</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:""