(5, 1, '2014-01-05 21:42:57', '2014-01-05 21:42:57', '<h2>Meet POTS</h2>\r\n<strong>POTS is the premier pediatric occupational therapy practice in Bergen County, providing cutting edge Occupational Therapy services to infants, children and their families since 1991.</strong>\r\n\r\nComprehensive evaluations of Sensory Integration, Handwriting, Gross Motor Skills and Fine Motor Skills are available for children birth through age 16. Treatment approaches include Sensory Integration, Floortime, Handwriting without Tears, Therapeutic Listening, Medek, and Interactive Metronome. We also offer School and Camp Consultations. Many of our staff members are SIPT Certified and Board of Education-approved and have numerous other certifications.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2014-01-11 19:37:59', '2014-01-11 19:37:59', '', 0, 'http://dev.pots.com/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
